</paragraph>
<paragraph blockId="49.[151,1437,150,971]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">
Note. The single specimen in coll. Lederer (MFNB) is the 
<typeStatus box="[845,947,691,717]" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">holotype</typeStatus>
: “[...] bei 
<collectingRegion box="[1055,1128,691,717]" country="Lebanon" name="Beyrouth" pageId="49" pageNumber="50">Beirut</collectingRegion>
